				<td colspan="2"><span>I suspect fewer than you would think...
<br />

<br />
Once we realized how effective these songs were during raids, we did a quick survey in the guild and found that a quarter of our bards hadn't completed these quests.
<br />

<br />
I have both arias on both of my bards, but completing the quests was a real pain the second time around (see the &quot;Stockpiling Erudite Meat&quot; thread in the Jonathan's Whistling Warsong forum) due to the unpredictable drop rates.
<br />

<br />
Get a good wind modifier and sing these songs on raids and you'll be a hero, especially if your clerics don't have their Radiant Cures or they're waiting on recast (3 minutes?) and some DoT is killing the main tank, the healers, et cetera.</span></td>
